snippet.title: Alaskan Truck Simulator Gameplay Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2021
snippet.description: Here's some brand new gameplay footage from Road Studio's Alaskan Truck Simulator, which is coming to PC in Q1 2022, with consoles to follow.
